# Project Phoenix → Bulkhead τ migration redirects.
#
# Phase 4 of the public-rebrand rollout (2026-05-01). Frozen paper artifacts
# have been mirrored to /bulkhead-tau/generated-papers/ (HTML) and
# /bulkhead-tau/generated-papers-src/ (markdown) by publish_paper.py. These
# 301s send legacy /project-phoenix/... paper URLs to their new homes,
# preserving slugs.
#
# Pages OTHER than the generated paper artifacts (philosophy.html,
# architecture.html, etc.) are intentionally NOT redirected — the
# project-phoenix landing remains as the engineering-core surface for now,
# per the in-steps rollout decision (option B).

RedirectMatch 301 ^/project-phoenix/(generated-papers|generated-papers-src)/(.+)$ /bulkhead-tau/$1/$2
